  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The conversion of the existing residential unit with a total floor area of less than 125sqm would not maintain the supply of larger homes in the borough.  The proposed self-contained flats would provide a substandard level of living accommodation by virtue of their inadequate internal floor area, inadequate room sizes and storage space, inclusion of a single person unit, inadequate amount of natural light or outlook and lack of amenity space. The proposal is therefore contrary to Policy 3.5 of the London Plan, Policy CS12 of the Islington Core Strategy, Policies DM2.1, DM3.3 and DM3.4 of the Islington Development Management Policies 2013, and the guidance contained within the London Plan Housing SPG."
